description.displayText: Last year, Elizabeth took care of my daughter (it was a nanny share). She is an amazing, engaging, fun, reliable and responsible nanny. I would hire again Elizabeth and definitely recommend her!
description.originalText: Last year, Elizabeth took care of my daughter (it was a nanny share). She is an amazing, engaging, fun, reliable and responsible nanny. I would hire again Elizabeth and definitely recommend her!

description.displayText: Elizabeth is fantastic. She really treated our daughters like family; so much love! They went on adventures, played in the park, did arts and crafts, read stories, and even brought them home with face paint some times! She was great with our infant and her older sister, so I can confidently recommend her for all ages. If we still needed child care, we wouldn't hesitate to work with her again. Book her while you can.
